trans-unit.source: Contains the data sent to the tracking service by the runtime tracking infrastructure when it matches a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Contém os dados enviados para o serviço de acompanhamento pela infraestrutura de controle de tempo de execução quando ele corresponde uma <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: It is also used in the return list of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*> property.
trans-unit.target: Ele também é usado na lista de retorno de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*>propriedade.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance.WorkflowEvents*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When the runtime tracking infrastructure matches a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, it sends a WorkflowTrackingRecord to the tracking service over the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> associated with that tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Quando a infra-estrutura de controle de tempo de execução corresponde um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>em um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>, envia um WorkflowTrackingRecord para o serviço de controle sobre o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel>associada ao controle de serviço.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingChannel> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: The tracking service can perform whatever action is necessary on the data in the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: O serviço de acompanhamento pode executar qualquer ação é necessária nos dados no registro de controle.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord"></xref> class by using the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent"></xref> value, <xref:System.DateTime>, number, and <xref:System.EventArgs>.

trans-unit.source: `eventDateTime` is expressed in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: `eventDateTime`é expresso em tempo Universal Coordenado (UTC).

trans-unit.source: `eventOrder` is guaranteed to be unique within the workflow instance; however, it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: `eventOrder`é garantido para ser exclusivo dentro da instância de fluxo de trabalho; No entanto, não é garantido para ser sequenciais.

trans-unit.target: A ordem relativa em que o evento de status de fluxo de trabalho associado a este registro de controle ocorreu na instância de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an <xref:System.EventArgs> that contains additional data associated with certain types of workflow status events.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um <xref:System.EventArgs>que contém os dados adicionais associados com determinados tipos de eventos de status do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: For most workflow status events, EventArgs is a null reference (`Nothing`); however, for certain kinds of workflow status events the runtime tracking infrastructure uses EventArgs to return additional data about the workflow status event.
trans-unit.target: Para a maioria dos eventos de status do fluxo de trabalho, EventArgs é uma referência nula (`Nothing`); no entanto, para determinados tipos de eventos de status do fluxo de trabalho a infra-estrutura de controle de tempo de execução usa EventArgs para retornar dados adicionais sobre o evento de status do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> values that correspond to these special workflow status events and the type of object returned in EventArgs for each of these workflow status events.
trans-unit.target: A seguinte tabela lista o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>valores que correspondem a esses eventos de status especial do fluxo de trabalho e o tipo de objeto retornados em EventArgs para cada um desses eventos de status do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the date and time that the workflow tracking event occurred.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a data e hora em que ocorreu o evento de rastreamento de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DateTime> is Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.DateTime>é o tempo Universal Coordenado (UTC).</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Essa propriedade é definida pelo tempo de execução de infra-estrutura de rastreamento.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that indicates the date and time that the workflow status event occurred.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.DateTime>que indica a data e hora em que ocorreu o evento de status do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates the order in the workflow instance of the workflow status event that matched the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um valor que indica a ordem em que a instância de fluxo de trabalho do evento de status do fluxo de trabalho que correspondem a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: EventOrder indicates the relative order in the workflow instance of the workflow status event that matched the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder indica a ordem relativa em que a instância de fluxo de trabalho do evento de status do fluxo de trabalho que correspondem a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: EventOrder is unique within a workflow instance, but it is not guaranteed to be sequential.
trans-unit.target: EventOrder é exclusivo dentro de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho, mas não é garantido que ele seja sequencial.

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Essa propriedade é definida pelo tempo de execução de infra-estrutura de rastreamento.

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates the order of the workflow status event in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Um valor que indica a ordem do evento de status do fluxo de trabalho na instância de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of workflow status event associated with the tracking record.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o tipo de evento de status do fluxo de trabalho associado ao registro de controle.

trans-unit.source: `TrackingWorkflowEvent` contains one of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> values indicating the kind of workflow status event that was matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure and caused the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> to be sent.
trans-unit.target: `TrackingWorkflowEvent`contém uma da <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>valores indicando o tipo de evento de status do fluxo de trabalho que foi correspondido pela infraestrutura de controle de tempo de execução e fez o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>seja enviado.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>

trans-unit.source: It reflects the current status of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Ele reflete o status atual da instância do fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: A workflow instance emits workflow status events only when the status of the workflow instance changes, and, therefore, a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> can be matched only when a workflow status change occurs.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância de fluxo de trabalho emite eventos de status do fluxo de trabalho somente quando o status da instância do fluxo de trabalho é alterado e, portanto, um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>pode ser correspondido somente quando ocorre uma alteração de status do fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>

trans-unit.source: This property is set by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Essa propriedade é definida pelo tempo de execução de infra-estrutura de rastreamento.

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Uma da <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent"> </xref> valores.
